 ############################
 COMMON GRUB INFO
 ############################

 To edit for example timeout you must open the next file
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | /etc/default/grub        						|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 And print something like
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | GRUB_TIMEOUT=60                    					|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 then you must print
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 |  # update-grub            						|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
